{"tid":284381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"堅尼地城站有賊仔 偷走警員簽到簿","createTime":"2017-06-15T00:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T01:22:15.000Z","uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cef3831e36048a05f24e6f7fda05b9afe8a94c8b","tid":284381,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T00:57:35.000Z","msg":"港鐵堅尼地城站發生簽到簿失竊案，警方鐵路警區人員於上周三(7日)下午巡經該站時，發現一鐵箱內的簽到簿懷疑被盜去。警員一度在附近搜索但沒有發現。案件暫列盜竊，交由西區警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲任何人士，如目擊有人在堅尼地城站偷竊簽到簿，或有資料提供，可致電36606627與西區警署人員聯絡。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56828995&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56828995%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170614&d=OYG%2FiSkxWfcRSRGquJGKgf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=74b14324\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56828995%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170614&h=5246cf55\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56828995&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170614</a>"},{"pid":"053fba85873dcdeb4f194318fe2451daac646049","tid":284381,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T01:02:11.000Z","msg":"被狗叼走？"},{"pid":"236ee519711f7cbaa3328b0cb0e6f1f08c2620dd","tid":284381,"uid":42921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T01:02:44.000Z","msg":"唔俾人發現簽到簿造假有乜方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2776e1a6cdb8d62e3c6d87fbb01eb8784cbf30","tid":284381,"uid":74796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T01:20:47.000Z","msg"